title: EXTRA: Jobs, Moore Withdraws Fed Candidacy
itunes:title: EXTRA: Jobs, Moore Withdraws Fed Candidacy
description:
Kevin discusses Friday's jobs numbers and Stephen Moore's decision to withdraw his candidacy for a seat on the Federal Reserve board a day before insisting in an interview with Bloomberg News that he was “all in” for the job. Guests include: Mattie Duppler, Senior Fellow at the National Taxpayers Union an former Former Coalitions Director for the House Republican Conference and Louise Schiavone, Journalist and Senior Lecturer at Johns Hopkins University CAREY Business School.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
